Connect Tree Privacy policy 
From this moment Graviton producer is refrenced as AmethystGames

App only collects data about user engagment and location through our advertisers.

AmethystGames is not responsible for any lost data including highscores.
AmethystGames is not responsible for any ads that are shown to the players.
AmethystGames does not take responsibility if this document is not avaible in case of (github.com) failure.

Amethyst Games can change privacy policy at any time but must inform users about the change either through app itself or Google Play Store.

